A grimy guam leaf is a herb that can be cleaned, requiring 3 Herblore, and yielding a guam leaf and 2.5 Herblore experience.

Grimy guam leaves can be harvested from herb patches after planting a guam seed, requiring 9 Farming.

Guam leaves are used to make Attack potions, Guthix rests, and guam tar.

A grimy guam leaf spawns in the Deep Wilderness Dungeon.

Date Changes
9 March 2017
(update)

The item's value was increased from 1 to 13.

(update)

  • The item was renamed from "Herb" to "Grimy guam leaf".
  • The item was made tradeable on the Trading Post/Grand Exchange.
  • The “Identify” option was changed to a “Clean” option.
25 February 2013
(update)
  • The item was renamed from "Grimy guam" to "Herb".
  • The "Clean" option was changed to an "Identify" option.

(update)
